Miscellaneous description
__________________________________________________________________

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_WindowingFunctions_Miscellaneous|
 * This plugin applies a window (weighting function) to each of the channels of the
 * input signal. Several windows are available. Note that the window is applied 
 * separately per each chunk and each channel. It does not 'slide' over the streaming data.
